article.linkText: Wicks propels Incarnate Word to 76-67 victory over Lamar
article.story: SAN ANTONIO -- — Sky Wicks finished with 19 points and 11 rebounds to power Incarnate Word to a 76-67 victory over Lamar on Monday night. Alex Anderson added 16 points and five rebounds for the Cardinals (8-16, 3-8 Southland Conference). Dylan Hayman scored 15. Terry Anderson finished with 22 points to pace the Cardinals (13-11, 7-4). Errol White totaled 10 points and nine rebounds. Janko Buljic added 10 points and six rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
